          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Liquid molecular para-hydrogen in Al alloy contailer",
                "of 55mm diameter, 2.5 mm thickness, fixed to a copper",
                "thermal reservoir. Inside the scattering cell, out of",
                "the neutron path, a solid catalyst Cr(2)O(3)- Al(2)O(3)",
                "was inserted to increase the rate of conversion from",
                "ortho- to para-hydrogen. T=16.0 K , the pressure",
                "0.3 bar. Estimated composition of 99.96% of",
                "para-hydrogen. Sample thickness 2.66 mm .",
                " Two vanadium thin foils before and after sample -",
                " to monitor the neutron beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
